Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:05.60,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I show you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.20,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:12.90,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,...what's under this eyepatch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:19.74,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,An artificial eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:23.51,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,My left eye is a doll's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:27.08,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It can see things that \Nshould remain unseen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.50,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,so I usually keep it covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.86,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:38.20,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,This might not be a good place for you, \Nsince you're not used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:39.67,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Not a good place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.80,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The dolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:50.10,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Dolls are hollow, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:54.85,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Completely hollow, in body and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:58.86,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,That void connects them with death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:03.74,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But hollow things seek to fill their emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:10.25,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel as though this \Nplace is drawing something out of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:11.75,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.24,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,We should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:17.50,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It's more comfortable upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:21.46,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you live around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:22.85,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:27.76,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,That thing about "Yomi at Twilight"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:29.96,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the name of this shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:36.44,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Feel free to drop in. -Studio M
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.32,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What is Studio M?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:36.44,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Kirika's studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.21,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It's on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.51,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kirika?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.82,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The person who makes these dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:48.24,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The ones in the basement, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.96,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think they're all Kirika's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.96,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why does that doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:02.28,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,...look so much like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:04.34,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:10.24,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,When I first met you, \Nweren't you holding a doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:11.35,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:17.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a girl died \Nat the hospital that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:19.07,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Was it for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.74,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:27.77,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think her name was Misaki, or Masaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:29.49,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:34.61,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.81,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Apparently, she was an only daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:44.88,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so her parents were devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:50.76,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:53.27,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Why indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:57.56,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no other customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.28,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have something else to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.41,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:14.10,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,A few things seem strange to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.57,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:19.04,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you not to get close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.91,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But it may be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:23.94,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.26,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know a thing about it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:31.72,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,There's an old story in this town...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:36.30,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,...about the class 3 of 26 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:39.99,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing nobody has told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:48.16,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,There was a student in that class...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:51.28,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,...who excelled in sports and her studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.54,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,She was kind to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:57.52,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,She was loved by teachers \Nand students alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:04.09,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But shortly after starting 9th grade, she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.67,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:10.57,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The story I heard said she was in \Na plane crash with her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.56,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But there are several other theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.48,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Some say it was a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:17.31,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Others claim she died in a house fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:22.90,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, everyone in the \Nclass was terribly shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.59,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,They were overcome with grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:31.32,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But then, suddenly, someone said,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:34.08,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,"She isn't dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:37.41,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,He pointed at her desk and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:39.54,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,"Look, she's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:43.83,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,See? She's alive and well."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:50.84,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Then, other students started \Nsaying the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.57,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,"It's true, she's not dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.75,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,That behavior spread through
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:00.01,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,the rest of the class, like a chain reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.79,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't want to believe the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:07.25,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't want to accept the cruel reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.36,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can relate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:15.41,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the class \Ncontinued with that act,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:19.24,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,insisting that the girl was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:22.04,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Even the homeroom teacher \Ntook their side, declaring,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:24.63,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,"It's true, she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:28.73,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,So all of you should continue \Nto work hard as a team,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:31.97,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,until the day you all graduate together."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.85,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The principal even arranged to have her seat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:38.61,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,included in the graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:40.89,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... a true story?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.26,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Then, after graduation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:46.55,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,everyone gathered in the \Nclassroom for the class photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:49.03,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The whole class, including the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:54.08,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But when they looked at the \Nphoto, they noticed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:56.14,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,There in the photo, off to the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:58.79,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,they could see the girl \Nwho should have been gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:02.09,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Her face was deathly pale,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:04.29,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,but she smiled like all the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:05.91,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.55,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The student who died...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:13.01,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,...was named Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:23.23,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,There's more to this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.11,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.76,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.62,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:42.74,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a little sidetracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:44.82,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.23,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I hate those devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:56.80,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You can be found, and caught, anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.97,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,It's closing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.48,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Please go on home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.74,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}1998 Midterm Exam Schedule\NGrade 9 Exam Dates\NMath | Science\NSocial Studies | Japanese
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.95,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Once exams are over, \Nwe start career counseling...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:23.13,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Having to discuss that \Nformally with a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:25.28,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,is so depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:29.77,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,These days, high school \Nacceptance rates are over 95%.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:30.88,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:33.26,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,There's a high school out \Nthere even you could get into.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.23,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Is that supposed to encourage me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:37.33,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,That was my intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:39.72,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you gonna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.02,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,West High.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.69,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Are your grades that high?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:49.73,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:50.52,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.61,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.36,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:01.58,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, you're stuck \Nwith me until graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.66,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your strength up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:04.20,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're stuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:07.55,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,We've been together since 2nd grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:09.95,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,We're even neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.52,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,When we were kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.30,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,we did all kinds of stupid stuff together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.37,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,But now he's turned into \Nthis pseudo-honors student
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:17.42,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,who can't keep up with my improv.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:21.67,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,To me, it just looks like \Nyou haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:23.94,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:25.93,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:31.77,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,I know things about you \Nthat even you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.75,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.07,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we're stuck with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:41.75,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:45.50,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you gonna do about high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:47.34,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:48.12,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:51.26,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,My dad will be back in Japan by next spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:52.82,Default,Kazami,0000,0000,0000,,You'll go to a private school there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:53.71,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:55.71,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's one way, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.21,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:01.43,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go to a private \Nschool in Tokyo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:04.30,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What school are you going to, Kouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.10,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,K High.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.74,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,K High, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.19,Default,Nakao,0000,0000,0000,,Akazawa, you're going to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:14.06,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,If I do, I suppose I'll live on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:21.39,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:23.67,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Sacred Heart something-or-other \Ngirls' school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.74,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I never said I wanted to go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:30.28,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Another one who's trying too hard for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.11,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:04.28,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you bring an umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:06.81,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:09.77,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.04,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:16.79,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to walk home with me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:21.85,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,My house is just past yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:26.57,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,But... I couldn't ask you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:34.48,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.43,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:46.65,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what do you do \Nfor class trips here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.78,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,We went to Tokyo, last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:51.35,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,We went to a big amusement park,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.52,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,and to the top of Tokyo Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:54.95,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,It was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.75,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You went to Tokyo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:13:00.71,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I love Tokyo. There are so \Nmany fun things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.97,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could go to school there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:04.68,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.39,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,My family can't afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:16.60,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, aren't class trips \Nusually a 9th grade thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:21.08,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Not here. We go during \Nthe 8th grade fall term.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:24.54,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Although, it used to be in \Nthe 9th grade spring term.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:26.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Used to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:28.20,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Um, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:31.09,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know when it changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:39.21,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't dislike rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:42.15,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sakuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:45.71,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What is Misaki like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.00,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.03,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.58,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever speak that name in class 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:11.12,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:14.65,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,But why—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:17.77,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Man, the rain's gotten worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.59,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you know the story
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.90,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,about the class 3 of 26 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:32.14,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,You actually believe stories like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.22,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.08,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.39,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard a rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.31,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,How much did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:48.33,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,A popular student suddenly died,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:53.49,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,and then she showed up in \Nthe class' graduation photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.84,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:15:00.13,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Only the first year...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:08.31,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you all look so serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:13.18,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Sakakibara knows about the first year...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.10,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.41,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:18.60,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:22.27,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. That's a delicate issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:27.28,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to keep it as quiet \Nas possible, for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.41,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep an eye on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.96,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:43.74,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:51.22,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you have exams next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:54.09,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Figure they'll be a breeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.19,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:59.45,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing all the studying I need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.60,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, sorry I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:08.61,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:11.61,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:17.08,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember which 9th \Ngrade class my mom was in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.42,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:29.32,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you know the story about \Nthe class 3 of 26 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.18,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:35.61,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:41.22,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I was asking about the \Nclass 3 of 26 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:47.06,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,That story's been swirling around for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:50.82,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there's a continuation to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:54.53,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know all of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:16:59.77,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You know it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:05.19,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,That type of story tends to get embellished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:11.39,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you should \Ntake it too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:16.56,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,There's a right time to \Nfind out about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:21.52,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko was in class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.84,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.77,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:47.82,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.13,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Entry Prohibited
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.47,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:03.93,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.56,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.56,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I called because I thought \Nyou were in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:11.03,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Akazawa looks like she's \Nabout to blow her top!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.31,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.19,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Sakaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:17.39,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with things that don't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.75,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:22.22,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:25.96,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,As for that story you asked about yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:28.21,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you everything next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:31.25,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,So, for the rest of this month, just—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:46.23,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's about that girl who died at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.95,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:51.23,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Her name was Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.87,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki, not Masaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.72,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,The "mi" used in "future,"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:57.51,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,and the "saki" meaning "blooming flowers."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:59.74,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,And it turns out her surname was Fujioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.78,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki Fujioka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:07.25,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to know about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.83,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.75,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.64,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,But someday, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:14.79,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:17.22,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you have exams coming up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:18.51,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:21.43,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,My little brother's studying like crazy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:22.73,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You have a brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:24.01,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Two, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:28.02,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,They're both total muscleheads, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.02,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,They don't care one bit about books!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.68,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they've ever read \Nanything except manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:34.52,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that just awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:37.53,Default,Board,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}May 26 (Tue.)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.92,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're always done early.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.27,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:11.07,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You left before the exam period \Nended yesterday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:12.69,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:16.02,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:22.33,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,So, her name was Misaki Fujioka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:24.69,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.27,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:30.91,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki was my cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:34.88,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,We used to be together all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.03,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,We were much more closely connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.53,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:47.73,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,About class 3 from 26 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.78,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's the rest of the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.88,0:20:55.82,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody will tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:20:57.37,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:00.01,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:03.66,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I've wanted to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:09.84,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Something I've been wondering \N since I transferred here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:13.50,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why does everyone in our class,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:15.96,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,even our teachers, act like you—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:18.09,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:20.98,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, Sakaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:22.84,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't mess with things that don't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:25.84,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:28.10,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:30.91,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:34.53,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,None of them can see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:43.61,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,What if you're the only \None who can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:46.66,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:49.84,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:54.30,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:21.52,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.97,0:24:50.05,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Put flesh.
